All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
ClassImplementor
The ClassImplementor class generates an implementation for a given class or interface.
ClassImplementor.MethodWrapper
A wrapper for a Method that provides functionality for code generation.
ClassImplementor.Rule
A rule for validating whether a class can be implemented.
ExecutableWrapper<T extends Executable>
An abstract wrapper for Executable elements such as methods and constructors.
ExecutableWrapper.DefaultValue
Represents a default return value for a specific type.
Implementor
A class that generates implementations of Java interfaces and abstract classes.
Impler
Generates class implementation by type token of class or interface.
ImplerException
Thrown by Impler when an error occurred.
JarImpler
Builds jar-file containing compiled implementation generated by Impler.
